WEBVTT

1
00:24:47.353 --> 00:24:50.413 
在星期六的早上疯狂地在房子里跑,
free to run wild through the house on Saturday mornings,

2
00:24:50.523 --> 00:24:53.492 
尽情地吃甜饼和喝牛奶...
free to have cookies and milk...

3
00:24:53.559 --> 00:24:55.959 
长那种白色的小胡子.
and get those little white moustaches.

4
00:24:56.028 --> 00:24:59.555 
只要在就不允许有人剥夺孩子的自由!
Nobody's gonna take a kid's freedom away while I'm around !

5
00:24:59.632 --> 00:25:01.964 
这么说你会带我们去了?
Does that mean you'll take us ?

6
00:25:02.034 --> 00:25:04.161 
不管有没有暴风雪,
Storm or no storm,

7
00:25:04.236 --> 00:25:07.171 
信天翁航班随时提供服务!
Albatross Airlines at your service !

8
00:25:09.075 --> 00:25:11.805 
旅客们必须系好安全带.
Passengers are requested to please fasten their seatbelts.

9
00:25:11.877 --> 00:25:15.369 
我们马上就要起飞了.
We'll be departing following our standard preflight maintenance.

10
00:25:15.448 --> 00:25:16.881 
谢谢.
Thank you.

11
00:25:16.949 --> 00:25:20.646 
放松肌肉, 让血液循环到我的大脑.
Loosen up, get the blood flowing up to the head.

